\id 2TH Ngindo Bible Version
\h 2 Akasesalonike
\toc1 Balua ja Paulo ja pabele kwa Sesalonike
\toc2 2 Akasesalonike
\toc3 2 Akas
\mt2 Balua ja Paulo ja pabele kwa
\mt1 Akasesalonike
\imt1 Kilongoi
\ip Balua ja 2 Sesolonike jiandikigwa na ndundame Paulo kwa Akasesolonike (Lipungu lya 1:1). Ajiandika balua jenje nyipi kubokapa balua ja 1 Sesolonike, chaka cha 51 kuboka pukubelekwa Kilisto. Paulo akiba tango Kukolinto pajiandika balua jenje kukikuta cha bandu abunhwamini Kilisto buku Sesolonike, ngi kikuta chakitumbula mwene mumwanja gwakwe gwa pabele (Itendwa 17:1-10). Ilengigwe mu kitabu chi Itendwa kutenda likanicha lyenie lichengigwa na Akayahudi na Akagiliki nduu.
\ip Likanicha lya Akasesolonike ngiliundigwa gambu gwa mangobu gukupela gano nu kubuja kwa pabele kwa Kilisto, gambu Paulo agaandike genia goa mubalua yakwe yoa kwa Akasesolonike. Nusu ja 2 Sesolonike nga magambu gu nhwalo gwa machoba gukupela gano. Uyo Paulo akelebwie nhwalo gwa chojo. Kila mundu apaligwa kamwa maengo gambu gwa chakulya (Lipungu lya 3:6-10).
\iot Agabi mukitabu
\io1 Paulo mubalua jakwe atumbwi kikilenga mwene na kapata abali akajakwe (Lipungu lya 1:1-2).
\io1 Kabe annumbite Nnoongo gambu gu kikuta cha bandu abunhwamini Kilisto buku Sesolonike nakajoe ku Nnoongo (Lipungu lya 1:3-12).
\io1 Mulipungu lya 2, Paulo alonge nhwalo gwa mangobu gukupela gano.
\io1 Kabe akelebwie nhwalo gwa chojo nambu bapaligwa kamwa maengo (Lipungu lya 3:1-15).
\io1 Paulo ajomoli kikipata abali kikuta cha bandu abunhwamini Kilisto (Lipungu lya 3:16-18).
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Ne Paulo na Silwano na Timoteo, tunhwandikilanga mabandu mamunhwamine Kilisto ba kwenio Kusesalonike, mammi mabandu ba Nnoongo Awawa bito na Angwana bito ana Yesu Kilisto.
\p 
\v 2 Tunnyopelanga ku Nnoongo Awabito na Angwana ana Yesu Kilisto bampe upeele na tengela.
\s1 Hukumu kingobu chu kuika Kilisto
\p 
\v 3 Makalongo twenga tupaligwe kunnumba Nnoongo machoba goa kwa magambu ginu mangweto, ipaligwe twe kutenda yene magambu imani nu kupalana kwinu kila mundu na nnyakwe jijonjeke kola.
\v 4 Nga kwa magambu twe tunnokeloke mangweto ikuta ya bandu ba Nnoongo mamunhwamine Kilisto. Mannyendekea kaamini Angwana nu kuimbalila kulaga nu kupotekigwa kukumpatanga.
\p 
\v 5 Genia goa galaya kube hukumu ja Nnoongo nga ejipaligwa, kupala mmonekane kutenda nnyeketeligwe kujingi mukingwana cha Nnoongo, nga magambu mpotekigwa nago.
\v 6 Nnoongo atenda andi pipaligwa, mabalepa kupotekigwa boa ababampoteka,
\v 7 mampaganga kupomolela mampotekigwa natwe uyo. Bitenda genia kingobu Angwana ana Yesu pabapakupitila kuboka kumbengu pamwe na akapakachi bakwe bukumbengu bina makakala.
\v 8 Apakuika na nimi ya mwoto kahukumu bandu abankana Nnoongo na abakana kujoa Nhwalo Gwambone gwa Angwana bito ana Yesu.
\v 9 Mabaukumigwa kupotekigwa machoba goa pangapela nu kubekigwa kutaali na Angwana na kibumo cha makakala gabe.
\v 10 Lichoba lyenie elyapakuika alumbigwa na bandu bakwe nu kuomongigwa na bandu abunhwamini, mangweto uyo mibaganga pamwe nabenia, magambu uchaili gwito nguaminika kwinu.
\p 
\v 11 Kwa magambu tunnyopelanga ku Nnoongo jwito machoba goa anhwotoye mangweto kuimbalila nu kutama kitamo chenie echankemilinge ntame, tunnyopa kwa makakala gakwe, alengenakie mawacho ginu gu kutenda gambone na kila liengo lya imani.
\v 12 Tujopa yene, kupala liina lya Angwana bito Ana Yesu lilumbigwa panakati jinu na mangweto mipata ichima kuboka kwakwe ku upeele gwa Nnoongo jwito na Angwana ana Yesu Kilisto.
\c 2
\s1 Mundu mmaja
\p 
\v 1 Gongo nga nhwalo gu kuika kwa Angwana bito ana Yesu Kilisto na twenga tukongana nnongi jakwe. Makalongo bito tunnyopa kukumpembela,
\v 2 makajojoke kuechukaje umwojo gwinu, andaje kube na mbwele kwa magambu kulenga lichoba lya Angwana liike. Pangaje ikita kutenda nhwalo gongo uboke mulondoi gwa bandu bange, matangacho andaje balua ejilengigwa jiboke kwito.
\v 3 Mundu akankoloyangaje kwa ndela jajoa, magambu lichoba lyenie liikaje mpaka lichoba lyale li kunkanalila Nnoongo lipitile na mundu jwakemigwa Mmaja abonekane, ojwapakujomale kualabigwa.
\v 4 Jwenio apakikikana kila kilebe echibikigongalela bandu nu kukikema Nnoongo, akitenda nkolongwa kukila kilebe kabe aijingila nu kutama Munyumba ja Nnoongo nu kukikema mwene kita Nnoongo.
\p 
\v 5 Bo, mmikombakelaje kutenda nannengalinge genia goa kingobu panakiba pamwe na mangweto?
\v 6 Nambu ngoe kibi kilebe chikinhwibila, namangweto mikimanyi kilebe chenie. Maliika lichoba lya Mundu Mmaja malibonekana kukingobu chikipaligwa.
\v 7 Magambu makakala ga Mundu Mmaja ga chili gakamu maengo ngoe nambu abonekana otije mpaka aboigwe oti ojwaibilikia.
\v 8 Penia Mundu Mmaja jwenio apapakuekuligwa, nambu Angwana ana Yesu pabapakuika bapakunkoma kuhuke gwa kano jabe nu kuntimba kukung'ala kwabe.
\v 9 Mundu Mmaja jwenoi aika kwa makakala gi Lichetani lilaya ikobo ndu ikuomongwa yuwangi,
\v 10 atumia uwangi gwa gwoa kwa kakoloya abaobanga. Angweto biobanga kwa magambu bapokilingeje ni kujipala kweli jakombolange.
\v 11 Yene Nnoongo babekangite bandu benia babe pae ja makakala guwangi, baamini yuwangi.
\v 12 Yene boa abakanite kujiamini kweli nambu bualali ubaja, bapakuhukumuligwa.
\s1 Mpambuligwe kupala nkoligwe
\p 
\v 13 Nambu ngoe tupaligwa kunnumba Nnoongo machoba goa kwa magambu ginu mangweto, mampaligwa na Angwana, magambu kuboka pitumbulaga Nnoongo ngampambula nkomboligwe kupete liengo lya Uhuke jwakwe, nu kummeka mme bandu bakwe bachwapi magambu ga kuamini kwinu kweli.
\v 14 Nnoongo ankemangita mangweto kupete Nhwalo Gwambone gutuntangachila kupala mmagange pamwe mukibumo cha Angwana bito ana Yesu Kilisto.
\v 15 Bai makalongo mma maha na magaagabale maboulo gutunnengila na gutunhwandakila.
\p 
\v 16 Tajopa Angwana bito bene ana Yesu Kilisto na ana Nnoongo Awabito abutupaile nu ku upeele gwabe ngubutupe tengela machoba goa pangapela ni lihyobalelo lya kweli,
\v 17 annimbie mwojo na ampegange makakala gi itendwa nu kulonge gambone.
\c 3
\s1 Mutujopele ku Nnoongo
\p 
\v 1 Pukujomolela makalongo bito mutujopele kupala Nhwalo gwa Angwana ujoanike chokwe na upokeligwe kuichima andi pibi kwinu mangweto.
\v 2 Uyo mutujopele kupala Nnoongo atukombole na bandu akabaja na bandu bina kijonga gambu boaje abaamini Nhwalo gongo.
\p 
\v 3 Angwana nga bina kuaminika. Bombe bannimbia nu kummeka tengela na Mmaja jola.
\v 4 Angwana bututenda tunhwamini mangweto kube mannyendekea kutenda agatunnengalinge.
\p 
\v 5 Angwana bijilongaleye myojo jinu mukulimanya lipalano lya Nnoongo nu kuimbalila kwatupi Kilisto.
\s1 Malagalakio gu kamu maengo
\p 
\v 6 Makalongo kulina lya Angwana bito ana Yesu Kilisto tunnagi, ntamanga kutali na bandu boa abunhwamini Kilisto ababi akata banga kengama malagilo gutulagile.
\v 7 Magambu mangweto mmene mmanyi kutenda mpaligwe kengama andi pututenda twenga. Twenga tukiba takakataje putukiba na mangweto,
\v 8 tulije chakulya kwa mundu panga lepa. Nambu ngutukamu maengo kilo na mui kukachana nu kulaga kupala tukabeje nhwigo ku mundu jwajoa kwinu.
\v 9 Tutenda genia ngiti tapaligwije kujangatigwa na mangweto, nambu kwa magambu kupala kunnayanga kilandanikio kwinu.
\v 10 Putukiba pamwe na mangweto ngutunnengela, “Mundu jwajoa jwakana kamu maengo, akalyeje chakulya.”
\p 
\v 11 Tulonge ilebe yene magambu tujoine kutenda babi bandu bange kati jinu akakata na kabe babi kamuje maengo, nambu angweto kikichumbuya kulonge minhalo ja bandu bange.
\v 12 Kuliina lya Angwana bito ana Yesu Kilisto nalagila na kakelebuyanga bandu benia babegange na majendo gambone nu kamu maengo kupala bapatange chakulya chabe bene akagweto.
\p 
\v 13 Nambu mangweto makalongo, makatotakaje kutenda gambone.
\v 14 Anda abi mundu kwenio jwanga agabala nhwalo gwito gwa balua jenje, mammekange pukongolou mundu jwenio na makatama nakweje, kupala abe naoni.
\v 15 Nambu mundu jwenio makantenda andi nngondwaje, nambu mankelebuya andi nnongo.
\s1 Chalamu chukujomolela
\p 
\v 16 Bene Angwana abaleta tengela, bampegange tengela machoba goa ku ndela jajoti jela. Na Angwana batame pamwe na mangweto.
\p 
\v 17 Ne Paulo, nampatanga abali kukunhwandiki ku luboko lwango namwene. Chene nga kiingi chango paandika kila balua, yene ngapaandika.
\p 
\v 18 Nnoongo ampegange upeele gwa Angwana bito ana Yesu Kilisto ube pamwe na mangweto mmoa.
